{
  "texts": [
    "This approach enables individuals to assess not only the AI system's intelligence but also their level of trust in it, alongside understanding its risks, capabilities, and limitations.",
    "Over time, this strategy aims to foster responsible engagement between users and AI systems.",
    "Finally, the possible implementations of the four criteria extend beyond the scope of this article.",
    "However, as an example, some application aspects of these criteria could be aligned with the capabilities of LLMs.",
    "Various experimental uses of this approach could be explored to analyze interactions between humans and AI systems, focusing on measuring the expected intelligence or certain intelligent characteristics anticipated in the system."
  ]
}